Delete parenthesis and its internals

Source: R/structure.R
delete_parenthesis.Rd

Delete parenthesis and its internals

Usage

delete_parenthesis(df)

Arguments

df

A dataframe analysed by MeCab

Value

A dataframe

Examples

library(magrittr)
library(dplyr)
data(review_mecab)
cols <- c("text_id", "\\u8868\\u5c64\\u5f62", "\\u54c1\\u8a5e", 
          "\\u54c1\\u8a5e\\u7d30\\u5206\\u985e1", "\\u539f\\u5f62") |>
         unescape_utf()
review_sudachi_a |>
  unescape_utf() |>
  dplyr::mutate(`:=`(text_id, as.numeric(text_id))) |>
  dplyr::filter(text_id < 5) |>
  dplyr::select(dplyr::all_of(cols)) |>
  print(n=80) |>
  delete_parenthesis() |>
  print(n=80)
